---
title: Succulent Balsamic Lamb Meatballs with Figgy Mint Sauce
description: Rich lamb meatballs get a boost of flavour from luxurious balsamic glaze for tonight's lamb roast-inspired dinner. Mashed potatoes, mint sauce and buttery peas all fall in line.
